{"tid":2188817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞：民主黨、公民黨等15人將據過半民意定去留，鄭松泰初步決定留任；鄭松泰：立場張圖扭曲我嘅說法。","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T13:01:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"559e0f7c04430059c195c41559c7ede0f567d73d","tid":2188817,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Background_Ojyhi_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FBackground_Ojyhi_1200x0.png&h=48812440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n民主黨早前委托香港民意研究所以民調決定，今日（4 日）公布方案，公民黨、工黨張超雄，和獨立民主派毛孟靜、邵家臻亦將跟從民調結果定去留。民主黨主席胡志偉指，經商討後去留與否僅倚賴單一門檻，即只計算支持者的過半意向，「只要有一半支持者要求我們離開，我們承諾必定服膺結果。」<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/議會去留-月內民調單一門檻-支持者過半意向定去留-民主黨-公民黨-張超雄等-15-民主派參與/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%80%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E5%AE%9A%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8-%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E7%AD%89-15-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=360980b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%80%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E6%84%8F%E5%90%91%E5%AE%9A%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8-%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E7%AD%89-15-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%2F&h=945288e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/議會去留-月內民調單一門檻-支持者過半意向定去留-民主黨-公民黨-張超雄等-15-民主派參與/</a><br />\n<br />\